    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Forecast brief on Scott v. McDougle — the Virginia Supreme Court challenge to the April 21, 2026 mid-decade redistricting amendment. Justice-by-justice analysis, vote bloc reads, scenario probabilities, the keystone McCullough vote, and what to watch before the merits ruling."
    />
    <meta property="og:title" content="SCOVA Forecast: Scott v. McDougle" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="Drafted May 7, 2026. Strike 60 / Uphold 35 / Punt 5. Justice-by-justice forecast on the Virginia Supreme Court redistricting case."
